      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Morgan Houppin</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/morgan-houppin-5587a0197/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/3b/MorganHouppin.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:MorganHouppin.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Morgan Houppin <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Morgan Houppin</b>,<br />\na French software developer and student at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/42_(school)\">42 Computer Training School</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lyon\">Lyon</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nAs computer chess programmer, Morgan Houppin is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/Stash\" title=\"Stash\">Stash</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Morgan_Houppin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73092\">New engine: Stash</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Morgan Houppin</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 14, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73930&amp;start=3\">Re: sort every moves or pickNext</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Morgan Houppin</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 14, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74918&amp;start=1\">Re: __builtin_popcountll doesn't bring any gain</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Morgan Houppin</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 28, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Population_Count\" title=\"Population Count\">Population Count</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69693&amp;start=27\">Re: Linux friendly engines at all levels</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Morgan Houppin</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 11, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Morgan_Houppin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/morgan-houppin-5587a0197/\">Morgan Houppin | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gitlab.com/mhouppin\">Morgan Houppin · GitLab</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/mhouppin\">mhouppin · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Morgan_Houppin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/morgan-houppin-5587a0197/\">Morgan Houppin | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.42lyon.fr/\">42 Lyon | École et formation d'informatique gratuite</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73092\">New engine: Stash</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Morgan Houppin</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 14, 2020</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301155431\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.015 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.017 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7499-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301155431 and revision id 21980\n -->\n"
